body:
So if you may not know some of the popular singed mains have quit playing singed (singed420, the guy on na with 2mill mastery on singed and a few other players, some on the oce server) because he is currently in a horrid state (worse than aatrox). after the ghost and colossus nerfs and the fact that every champion is building a edge of night singed is quiet possibly the worst champion in league. I&#039;m currently sitting on 470k mastery points with over 500 singed games in 3 seasons of league.

Us singed mains in season 5 knew singed was bad but he was not trash teir, in season 6 he just got worse and now in season 7 hes pretty much unplayable. &quot;if i had a gun at my head and was told to climb in ranked i would pick nasus, even though i am a singed one trick&quot;

You may say &quot;but what about the dark seal stacking&quot; mate we only use that to SURVIVE lane phase.

I have made a petition to have the information to show to riot that singed is in a really bad spot (because whenever we singed mains approach them about singed they tell us singed is op, or singed is in a great spot right now his win rate is solid (the only reason why singeds win rate is average is because only dedicated mains play him, regardless of how bad he is)

If you disagree with this, state your elo, your singed mastery points and years playing league before saying anything else.

Singed Needs A Change. {{champion:27}} {{item:3070}} {{item:3070}}
